name: "de pendejo a la popular del heat"
description:
Ricardus
Ricardus is the fusion between Ricardo Fort & Frida Kahlo, each edition can also have a shout out to other iconic celebrities.

"de pendejo a la popular del heat" is the second edition of the collection and it puts ricardus in a disco. In his arm we can see a tattoo that says "gianina" thats makes reference to one of the daughters of Diego Armando Maradona and is wearing wade's jersey, in reference to the city of miami, the place where ricardus loves to be.
